Event Description: WELCOME TO ONE OF THE FEW BRAND-NEW GULF FRONT HOMES FOR SALE ON THE WEST CENTRAL COAST OF FLORIDA. A rare and extraordinary offering, where cutting-edge design meets endless sea-to-sky vistas. Nestled on the exclusive barrier island of Casey Key, this newly constructed Modern Coastal estate by Modesta Homes defines luxury beachfront living. Positioned directly on the sand with unobstructed Gulf views, this striking residence offers 7,977 square feet of elevated, FEMA-compliant living space, showcasing the pinnacle of craftsmanship and architectural innovation. Built to the highest standards with concrete block construction, pilings, impact-rated windows and doors, and a four-stop elevator, every detail of this home has been thoughtfully curated for style, function, and resilience. Inside, soaring 24-foot ceilings welcome you into the grand foyer and great room, anchored by a dramatic floating staircase and a 24-foot feature fireplace wall. With 6 spacious en-suite bedrooms, state-of-the-art home theater, lounge, bar, and a wine wall, this home offers both grand entertaining and serene retreat. The chef’s kitchen is a design showpiece, featuring European cabinetry, dual waterfall-edge islands clad in book-matched 3cm quartz, and premium Sub-Zero & Wolf appliances. Dual laundry rooms, breakfast nook, and custom built-in vanities provide elevated everyday living. The primary suite is a private sanctuary, complete with a spa-like bathroom featuring a 71-inch freestanding tub, dual rainfall showers, a makeup vanity, and a 400 sq ft walk-in closet. Every bathroom throughout the home is appointed with bespoke cabinetry, quartz surfaces, and backlit mirrors. Designed to impress from every angle, the home is finished with smooth stucco, level 5 drywall, hardwood floors, imported tile, and integrated LED tray ceilings. A sleek rooftop terrace crowns the home, offering panoramic views of the Gulf and beyond. Step outside to your private resort: an expansive terrace with an oceanfront pool, floating spa, sun decks, outdoor fireplace, and fully equipped kitchen. Lush, tropical landscaping, Zoysia grass, and a concrete drive with turf inlays complete the impeccable exterior design. Sleek metal railings accentuate balconies and the rooftop for a modern edge. Set on a half-acre of prime waterfront, this property also includes deeded bay access across the street. This is coastal modern luxury at its finest—a rare opportunity to own a brand-new, Gulf-front estate on one of Sarasota’s most coveted stretches of sand.
